column16: David DeJesus pops out to third baseman Scott Sizemore.
Ryan Hanigan singles on a sharp line drive to left fielder Alfonso Soriano.   James Loney scores.    Wil Myers scores.
Logan Forsythe lines out sharply to left fielder Alfonso Soriano.
Sean Rodriguez pops out to shortstop Yangervis Solarte.
Wil Myers doubles (3) on a line drive to left fielder Alfonso Soriano.   James Loney to 3rd.
James Loney singles on a line drive to right fielder Ichiro Suzuki.
